1. Make a controller named StaticPages. Include home and help methods.
   $ rails generate controller StaticPages home help
2. Name routes for home and help
   get 'static_pages/home'
   get 'static_pages/help'
3. Update the static_pages/home and static_pages/help views
   home = <a href="http://www.railstutorial.org/">Ruby on Rails Tutorial</a>
   help = <a href="http://www.railstutorial.org/book"><em>Ruby on Rails Tutorial</em>
             book</a>.
